      "title": "3. 主线连接：Xw+b 的 shape 账本",
      "content": "核心词汇继续使用 `x`, `w`, `b`, `y_hat`, `y`, `L`。批量时用大写 `X` 表示许多 `x`：\n\n```text\nX = [[2, 3], [1, 4]]   shape (2, 2)\nw = [4, -1]            shape (2,)\nb = 5                  scalar\ny_hat = [10, 5]        shape (2,)\ny = [9, 7]             shape (2,)\nL = 2.5                scalar MSE\n```\n\n合同为 `y_hat = Xw + b`。其中内侧特征维 2 对齐，外侧样本维 2 被保留。目标不参与 `Xw+b`，只进入 MSE。",
      "en": "The shared shape ledger is `X: (2,2)`, `w: (2,)`, `X @ w: (2,)`, scalar `b`, `y_hat: (2,)`, and `y: (2,)`. In compact form `y_hat = Xw+b`. The contraction is `(Xw)_i = sum_j X_ij w_j`: feature axis j disappears after pairing with w, while sample axis i remains. For the first row, 4*2-1*3+5=10; for the second, 4*1-1*4+5=5. Targets [9,7] produce residuals [1,-2], squares [1,4], and MSE 2.5."
