      "title": "8. 代码翻译：向量化但仍可逐行核验",
      "content": "```python\nimport numpy as np\n\nX = np.array([[2.0, 3.0], [1.0, 4.0]])\nw = np.array([4.0, -1.0])\nb = 5.0\ny = np.array([9.0, 7.0])\n\nassert X.ndim == 2 and w.ndim == 1\nassert X.shape[1] == w.shape[0]\nweighted = X @ w\ny_hat = weighted + b\nresiduals = y_hat - y\nL = np.mean(residuals ** 2)\nprint(weighted, y_hat, L)  # [5. 0.] [10. 5.] 2.5\n```\n\n调试时可用 `X * w` 得到每行每列贡献，再沿 `axis=1` 求和。若误用 `axis=0`，会按列汇总并失去“每样本一个预测”的合同。\n\n### 代码基线与 shape 症状\n\n```python\nloop_predictions = []\nfor row_index, x in enumerate(X):\n    assert x.shape == w.shape\n    weighted_sum = 0.0\n    for feature, weight in zip(x, w):\n        weighted_sum += feature * weight\n    loop_predictions.append(weighted_sum + b)\nassert np.allclose(loop_predictions, y_hat)\n```\n\n外循环跨样本，内循环跨特征。`X @ w` 没有改变这个数学层次，只把循环交给数组实现。对固定小数据保留相等断言，可以发现 axis 或广播错误。\n\n| 症状 | 常见原因 | 最小检查 |\n|---|---|---|\n| 内维报错 | 特征数与权重数不同 | `X.shape[1] == w.shape[0]` |\n| 残差变 `(2,2)` | `(2,)` 与 `(2,1)` 交叉广播 | `y_hat.shape == y.shape` |\n| 数值顺序交换 | 样本行交换 | 样本 ID 与目标同步置换 |\n| shape 正常但首项非 10 | 列顺序错位 | 展开第一行贡献 |\n\n最后一种最危险，因为程序能够运行。shape 是必要证据，列语义是另一份必要证据。",
      "en": "The executable vectorized path creates X=[[2,3],[1,4]], w=[4,-1], b=5, y=[9,7], asserts X.ndim==2, w.ndim==1 and X.shape[1]==w.shape[0], then computes weighted=X@w, y_hat=weighted+b, residuals=y_hat-y, and L=mean(residuals**2). It prints [5,0], [10,5], and 2.5. X*w exposes contributions; summing axis=0 is wrong because it crosses rows.\n\n### Loop baseline and shape symptoms\n\nThe loop baseline iterates rows outside and paired features inside, asserts x.shape==w.shape, accumulates weighted_sum, adds b, and requires allclose(loop_predictions,y_hat). Inner-dimension errors check X.shape[1]==w.shape[0]; residual (2,2) checks y_hat.shape==y.shape; swapped values require sample IDs and targets to move together; correct shape but first result not 10 requires expanded first-row contributions. Shape is necessary, while column semantics is separate necessary evidence."
